    "Numerical analysis, results and correlationsAs mentioned in Sec.",
    "2, in the ABCD model various scenarios have been considered for the Z ′ couplings to fermions [1].",
    "One of them, the scenario A, consists in assuming flavour violating couplings of Z ′ only with left-handed fermions, obtained setting to zero the parameters in ( 36)- (37).",
    "The present study is based on this minimal scenario.The list of the parameters consists of the four entries in (35) and of the parameters of the CKM and PMNS matrices.",
    "The coupling g Z ′ is varied in the range g Z ′ ∈ [0.01, 0.1], and two cases are considered for the Z ′ mass, M Z ′ = 1 TeV and M Z ′ = 3 TeV."
